      "headings": [
        "Welcome, we are delighted that you have chosen to begin your stay in Groningen here!",
        "Asgard Hotel",
        "Meetings at the Asgard Hotel"
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Feast your eyes on our unique 1930s building in the heart of Groningen. Our design hotel features modern design elements and sustainable, ecological materials such as clay walls, design and art by Berber Geerts and others in our interior and architecture.",
        "During breakfast, we serve organic products from local entrepreneurs and farmers. We prefer quality over quantity and are happy to share this with you!",
        "Would you like to stay in Groningen for longer? Then choose one of our apartments. These are perfect for a longer stay or if you want the option of cooking for yourself.",
        "Our meeting room 'De Groene Kamer' is in a prime location, within walking distance of Groningen city centre and the central station. If you book a meeting package with us, you can use our room for up to 12 people.",
        "Would you like to hold a stylish meeting in our Green Room? Please contact us."
      ],
